				<tr>
					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Even if you simulate the whole instruction at once, it might be better to advance the time by 12 dots before the PPU sees a write, because scrolling has such tight timing.  The scrolling increment happens at dot 256 of a scanline, so you can treat it as if it happens 12 dots sooner and still avoid most scrolling glitches.</div>

					
